{"tid":538177,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"賺蝕問題求指教","createTime":"2018-01-23T11:46:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-23T12:07:06.000Z","uid":125261,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2818a357e52213492d8994339cfaf1bd4b8e3cba","tid":538177,"uid":125261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T11:46:44.000Z","msg":"假設以前用 $1 買左一隻股票共 10 股，付出左 $10<br />\n擺左佢一段時間後，總共收左 $5 股息<br />\n而家股價係 $1.5<br />\n<br />\n想問下，以下呢兩種計算賺幅，先正確？<br />\n<br />\nA. 賺幅係 100%<br />\n因為：總數付出左 $10，而家得到既野係 $15 (市值) + $5 股息 = $20<br />\n咁賺幅就係 (20-10)/10 = 100%<br />\n<br />\nB. 賺幅係 200%<br />\n因為：總共收到 $5 股息，手上既貨既持有成本就變成 $10 - $5 = $5, 或者每股既成本就係 $0.5<br />\n咁賺幅就係 1.5-0.5/0.5 = 200%<br />\n<br />\n純理論問題，實際上會有唔少手續費，印花稅，佣金等開支要計埋先真<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e658a09d5a316b86118a52e795f34e02f63eb8b","tid":538177,"uid":67823,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T11:51:12.000Z","msg":"B<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f025c956c7f927d1e7fcf9ecf185f06f78c674ac","tid":538177,"uid":253,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T11:51:52.000Z","msg":"B 點解係（1.5-0.5)/0.5<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71b4284b678ef81fb2369ed3c9b4b05b77b4b348","tid":538177,"uid":115344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T12:07:06.000Z","msg":"當然係A,用b 既話唔係長久而方便既計法。你當股息10蚊用b 計計就明。仲有十年後，你收既股息遠高於成本既話，點計？"}]}